item.description:
WESTLIFE - THE TWENTY TOUR: LIVE FROM CROKE PARK (CD)
The Twenty Tour - Live from Croke Park is a celebration of one of pop's most sensational comebacks. Filmed at Westlife's homecoming gig in summer 2019, this spectacular live show features Shane, Nicky, Mark and Kian at their very best, performing their greatest hits to the backdrop of the iconic Croke Park stadium in Dublin, Ireland. Includes incredible performances of all their hit singles, including 'Uptown Girl', 'You Raise Me Up', 'Flying Without Wings' and 'World Of Our Own', along with brand new tracks 'Hello My Love', 'Better Man' and 'Dynamite' to a sell-out crowd with spectacular staging, lights and effects.

Deluxe edition CD+DVD was released in 2020.
